mysql> show create table User;
+-------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Table | Create Table
                                                              |
+-------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| User  | CREATE TABLE `User` (
  `full_name` varchar(100) NOT NULL COMMENT 'full name of user',
  `email` varchar(100) NOT NULL COMMENT 'user''s email',
  `username` varchar(100) NOT NULL COMMENT 'username',
